        <p>The Font Properties dialog lets you apply multiple kinds of font formatting to the selected content in a topic all at once. In the Font Properties dialog, you can set the font type, size, style, color, and background color. You can also apply effects such as overline, underline, strikethrough, superscript, subscript, and smallcaps. Finally, there are advanced formatting settings, such as expanded or condensed letter and word spacing, as well as capitalization options.</p>
